Cook the pasta in boiling salted water following package directions until tender. Drain and rinse with cold water. In a large bowl, combine cooked pasta, celery, green and red bell peppers and red onion. In a small bowl, mix together the mayonnaise, Italian dressing, and Old Bay. Pour into pasta; mix well. Stir in the shrimp. Chill 2 hours if desired. Sprinkle with additional Old Bay just before serving, if desired.